name: COMMISSION ME
description:
Have an original piece by yours truly, just give me a subject, a price range, and a medium!

I'll make it happen!

Just message me to discuss the piece and then I will write up a description and list your artwork for sale!

name: STICKERS
description:
$1 for 2, new Christina Walker Art Stickers!

[3 inch stickers on white vinyl, can be used indoors or outdoors.]

name: WRAITH [PRINT]
description: <b>Because this was my most popular painting I've posted, I have decided to get prints made. This is a Pre-sale where the cost will be less than ordering the print after they come in. Prints are limited to 15. All prints are signed and embossed.

name: WRAITH [ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
First time painting on a black canvas, tried to keep the image on the simple side. Did not have any direction when I started the painting but it did end up as a bit of a specter...or wraith.


[Oil on black canvas, painting is not mounted in a frame, prints are also available.]

name: NATURAL [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
First attempt at still life in a long time, used a skull that a client gave me for the reference. A really fun painting I'll be a bit sad to see it go.


[Framed original oil, no prints will be made]

name: SLIMER [ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
My largest painting so far, Slimer! My take on our "Famous Monsters" theme at the Lucky Bamboo art gallery should include ghosts! Painting is without frame, no prints will be made.


[Painting is 24 inches by 35 inches.]

name: NOSFERATU [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Another "Famous Monster" for the Lucky Bamboo theme art gallery. Nosferatu! Classic Vampire, framed original on canvas board, no prints will be made. One of the first times messing with something close to a serious human form with oils.


[Painting fitted into dark ornate frame about 27 by 23 inches including frame.]

name: MARS ATTACKS! [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
A piece for the "Famous Monsters" theme at the Lucky Bamboo art gallery, everyone's favorite alien from Mars Attacks! Oil on canvas in fitted black frame, no prints will be made!


[Painting is 10 by 13 inches with the frame.]

name: A SEAHORSE [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Framed original oil painting of a sea horse, one I started a while and finished fairly recently once I had more practice with oils and glazing.


[No prints will be made, original painting is 12 by 12 inches and about 14 by 14 in the frame.]

name: WANDER [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Framed original oil painting, the first one I've completed in a while, so it's full of lose brush strokes and a blend of different colors. No prints will be made


[Painting in frame is 24 by 20 inches set in frame.]

name: SAILORS GRAVE [FRAMED ORIGINAL WATERCOLOR]
description:
Went with a darker nautical theme on this one, I really like how this one came out. ! Watercolor onon watercolor paper. Painting is fitted in custom matte and frame


[Painting is about 19 by 16 inches including the frame. prints are also available for sale. Fitted in frame with custom double matte.]

name: SAILORS GRAVE [PRINT]
description:
Went with a darker nautical theme on this watercolor and I really like how this one came out.


[Prints are signed numbered and embossed, one of 15. Painting is about 12 by 7 1/2 inches, prints also have an inch white border for matting.]

name: ROSA SKULL [FRAMED ORIGINAL WATERCOLOR]
description:
Original watercolor on watercolor paper, A skull with flowers with an ornate black background. Based on a reference I drew a while ago for an arm piece for a client, super fun watercolor! Prints are also available.


[Painting is about 8 by 11 inches. Fitted in a custom dark matte and dark antique style frame. About 15 and 1/2 by 18 inches with the frame.]

name: ROSA SKULL [PRINT]
description:
Prints of an original watercolor I did, a skull with flowers and an ornate black background. Based on a reference I drew a while ago for an arm piece for a client, this was a super fun watercolor!


[Painting is about 8 by 11 inches with a white border for matting. Prints are 1 of 15, all are embossed, signed and numbered.]

name: BARN OWL [ORIGINAL IN OIL]
description:
Original oil painting of a barn owl, 3rd painting done at the artist workshop in Grants Pass. I've always loved owls and I love how this one came out!


[Original is signed, prints are also available for sale]

name: BARN OWL [PRINT]
description:
Print of an original oil painting of a barn owl, 3rd painting done at the artist workshop in Grants Pass. I've always loved owls and I love how this one came out! Prints have been in high demand so get them while you can! Only 12 will be made.


[Prints are on textured matte paper with a white borfer for framing, they are sign numbered and embossed. Print quality is super close to the original! With border each print is about 14 x 14 inches.]

name: IN PASSING [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Original oil painting on canvas, started in Grants Pass at a painting seminar with Jeff Gogue. First painting with the new technique and I love how it came out!

[Original is signed and painting measures 12 by 24 inches. Painting is fitted in think simple black frame and ready to hang]

name: IN PASSING [PRINT]
description:
Print of my first oil painting titled "In Passing" these are limited to 12 signed and embossed prints, they are slightly smaller than the original painting, but look amazingly close to the original.


[Prints are signed, numbered and embossed. On textured matte paper with a a white border for framing. Prints including border are 12 x 22 inches.]

name: NOH MASK [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Another Hannya or Japanese Noh Mask, they are always fun to paint and it is always so easy to make the next one different than the last.


[Original framed Hannya mask, in a ornate dark brown and black frame, painting is signed and no prints will be made. The painting is 12 by 24 inches in size without the frame.]

name: BIRD OF PREY [ORIGINAL ACRYLIC]
description:
An original painting of a barn owl, acrylic on unfinished wood. Was actually a reference for a tattoo that I had not have a chance to do yet. Was a quick but fun color study.


[Painting is signed and ready to hang, no prints will be made. Painting is about 16 by 10 inches. Acrylic on wood with a clear coat to seal it.]

name: LINKS ADVENTURE [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Another painting for a video game themed art show! Link from the Legend of Zelda, framed original watercolor.

[Framed and signed, actual painting is about 8 inches in diameter, prints on card stock are also available. Prints are embossed and numbered.]

name: LINKS ADVENTURE [PRINT]
description:
Prints of another painting for a video game themed art show! Link from the Legend of Zelda, was original watercolor on watercolor paper.

 [Print is signed, actual painting is about 8 inches in diameter, prints are on card stock,embossed and numbered.]

name: SUPER MARIO BROS [FRAMED ORIGINAL SET]
description:
Set of 2 original framed watercolor paintings. This set was done for an art show with a video game theme! A classic representation of some classic game characters!

[No prints will be made, this is a set of 2 original watercolors both matted, framed and ready to hang. Actual painting size about 6 by 4 inches, each painting in frame about 10 1/4 inches by 8 1/2 inches.]

name: MATRYOSHKA [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Framed original oil painting of a Matryoshka doll, also known as Russian nesting doll, refers to a set of wooden dolls that stack/nest inside each other.


[Original is signed and in a black frame, no prints will me made, the painting is 16 by 20 inches without the frame. Mixed media with a paint marker outline background]

name: OTAFUKU MASK [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Also know by Otakame, Otafuku means "Much Good Fortune" or a symbol for a long life. Otafuku is always seen smiling and is told to bring happiness and good fortune to any man she marries. I thought this happy mask would be a nice change to all the ominous paintings I tend to create.


[Original framed oil painting, no prints will be made. Oil on canvas, painting is about 11 by 14 inches not counting the frame.]

name: THE SNAIL [ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Original oil painting, actually my second snail I've painted! Just as fun as the first!


[Original is signed and not in a frame, no prints will be made painting is 12 by 12 inches]

name: MINI WATERCOLOR SET [FRAMED ORIGINALS]
description:
A Magnolia flower, Cherry Blossom and Skull, with stippled black background originals are signed and framed! Great for a gift!

[Set of 3 mini original watercolors, no prints will be made. Sold as a set while paintings are in stock. 2 smaller paintings about 3.5 inches in frame, Magnolia about 6 3/4 high in frame.]

name: CHERRY BLOSSOM MINI PAINTING [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Framed original Cherry Blossom flower mini watercolor painting. A cute flower in an ornate blue frame with a simple black stippled background. Really fun to paint! A great gift, thanks for looking!


[Original is signed, no copies will be made. Actual painting is about 2.3 inches in diameter, with frame about 3.5 inches in diameter]

name: SKULL MINI PAINTING [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Framed original Skull mini watercolor painting. A colorful skull in an ornate brown frame with a simple black stippled background. Really fun to paint! A great gift, thanks for looking!


[Original is signed, no copies will be made. Actual painting is about 2.3 inches by 2.3 inches, with frame about 3 1/4 inches tall and wide]

name: MAGNOLIA MINI PAINTING [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Framed original Magnolia flower mini watercolor painting. A cute flower in an ornate black frame with a simple black stippled background. Really fun to paint! A great gift, thanks for looking!


[Original is signed, no copies will be made. Actual painting is about 2.3 inches by 3.3 inches, with frame about 6.75 inches tall and 4.75 inches wide]

name: PLAGUE MASK [FRAMED ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Cool toned Plague mask with a warm red background in custom red spotted frame, Original painting no prints will be made.


[Painting is signed and is ready to hang! with frame about 12 by 24 inches. Painting is on canvas board]

name: GEISHA WITH WAVES [PRINT]
description:
Print of a watercolor I did in 2011, a color study for a thigh piece I am currently tattooing on myself.


[Print is one of 15 all prints are signed, numbered and embossed.]

name: KOKESHI DOLL [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Original oil painting of a cute Kokeshi doll, painting is in custom built frame and is ready to hang! Painting is about 15 1/2 by 9 1/2 with the frame.


[No prints will be made, oil on canvas board]

name: MANEKI-NEKO [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Framed painting of a Luck Cat in oil on canvas board, framed and ready to hang! No prints will be made.

[Size of painting in frame is about 27 inches by 23 inches]

name: PEACOCK FEATHER [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Original peacock feather in oil on canvas, comes mounted in ornate black frame, no prints will be made.

[Original is signed painting is about 15 1/2 by 13 1/2 inches with the frame.]

name: ESCARGOT [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
I've always wanted to paint a snail! Not sure why, I just love shells in general, I love this piece! It will be hard to let go of. No prints will be made.

[Painting is set in frame and signed, painting is 10 by 10 inches and in with the frame is 17 by 17 inches .]

name: HANNYA ON CLAYBOARD [ORIGINAL OIL]
description:
Original oil painting of a Hannya mask in earthy colors, my first time using clayboard and I love how it came out!

[Painting is signed and comes in black metal frame]

name: BLACK AND GRAY HANNYA [FRAMED ORIGINAL WATERCOLOR]
description:
Original Hannya painting that is black and gray featuring Japanese finger waves and a Hannya mask. One of my first watercolor paintings I did

[Painting about 10 x 14 inches,15 1/2 by 19 inches counting the frame. Gloss white frame with a custom black matte.]

name: BLACK AND GRAY HANNYA  [PRINT]
description:
Original Hannya painting that is a black and gray water color, on water color paper and painting is about 10 by 14 inches with a white border for matting.

[These are signed and numbered prints on card stock]

name: WATERCOLOR SKULL SET [SET OF 3 PRINTS]
description:
Set of all 3 watercolor skull paintings! A good way to save and get all three pieces that I love!

[Prints are all signed and numbered, sets available while quantities last, all have white borders and are on white cardstock.]

name: CHERRY BLOSSOMS AND SKULL [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Matted and framed original watercolor I did as reference for a tattoo, a fun little painting! A skull surrounded by cherry blossoms.
[Painting is about 11x8 1/2 inches, original is signed and ready to hang! Prints are also available]

name: CHERRY BLOSSOMS AND SKULL [PRINT]
description:
Print of a watercolor I did as reference for a tattoo, a fun little painting! A skull surrounded by cherry blossoms.
[print is about 11x8 1/2 inches, with plenty of white border to allow for matting, 1 of 25 prints made, signed and number]

name: SKULL AND MAGNOLIA [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Framed original watercolor I did as reference for a tattoo, a fun little painting! A skull with magnolia flowers.
[painting is about 11x8 1/2 inches, matted and framed original is signed prints are available]

name: SKULL AND MAGNOLIA [PRINT]
description:
Print of a watercolor I did as reference for a tattoo, a fun little painting! A skull with magnolia flowers.
[print is about 11x8 1/2 inches, with plenty of white border to allow for matting, 1 of 25 prints made, signed and number]

name: KEYHOLE SKULL [PRINT]
description:
Inspired quite a bit after a trip to Europe, a watercolor skull with an ornate keyhole, i'm in love with piece, and think these prints will sell fast.

[Prints are signed, numbered and do not have watermark, the painting is 8 1/2 by 5 inches with 1/4 border for framing, only 20 prints will be made.]

name: OWL IN OIL [ORIGINAL]
description:
Original oil painting of an owl, which turns out are a very fun thing to paint!

[Original is signed, painting is about 8 by 8 inches in size.]

name: ANIMAL SKULL [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Animal skull, watercolor on watercolor paper, framed and matted original.
[Painting is about 14 by 11 inches in a 8 by 10 matte, signed and ready to hang!]

name: RED HANNYA MASK [ORIGINAL]
description:
Original Japanese Hannya mask painting, acrylic on canvas, painting is signed and ready to hang!
[Canvas measures about 18 by 24 inches.]

name: GREEN HANNYA WATERCOLOR [PRINT]
description:
This is actually a print of my first watercolor, a green Hannya with cherry blossoms and Japanese finger waves.

[Print is signed, numbered and is one of 15, the print is about 17 by 12 inches in size. 2nd image is an example of the painting framed and matted.]

name: SKULL AND FILIGREE [ORIGINAL]
description:
Warm toned skull in oil, my 2nd oil painting, the painting is 12 inches by 12 inches on stretched canvas.

[No prints will be made]

name: SWALLOW AND BLOSSOMS [ORIGINAL]
description:
Original swallow and cherry blossom painting, it about 7 by 11 inches painted on a piece of wood that is ready to hang!
[acrylic paint, original is signed]

name: CHERRY BLOSSOMS [ORIGINAL]
description:
A couple of cherry blossoms on a black background, painting wraps on sides of ready to hang painting. No prints will be made of this painting, a guaranteed one of a kind!
[Painting is acrylic and is about 12 by 6 inches in size.]

name: KOI FISH [PRINT]
description:
Japanese style orange and black Koi fish with cherry blossoms. print on sommerset velvet paper which makes it look a lot like the original, print has 1/4 inch border for matting. Print is 22 by 11 inches in size.

[ Prints are limited, numbered, sold in order, and signed. Only 30 printed]

name: MOVEMENT [COMMISSIONED]
description:
Black and gray skull, acrylic on canvas, another commissioned piece! About 18 inches tall.
[no prints will be made]

name: CRANE AND WAVES [PRINT]
description:
I've always loved paper cranes, and how simple but appealing they look, this simple drawing was definitely a fun one, and one of my favorites. This is a print of the original.

[About 8 by 9 1/2 inches, watermark not on print, the print on card stock, matte and frame not included. Prints are limited, numbered, sold in order and signed. 15 prints made]

name: IRIS [PRINT]
description:
One of 10 prints made, on cardstock, a cute purple Iris watercolor I did.

[Watermark not on print, numbered and signed, print is 6 by 11 inches with a 1/4 inch border]

name: QUAN YIN [FRAMED ORIGINAL]
description:
Framed original painting of Quan Yin, finished at the Park City Tattoo Convention in August of 2012 at the live painting. Painting is mounted in silver ornate frame.


[No prints will be made, painting is about 11 1/2 inches by 10 inches in the frame.
